name: Onomatopick
desc: You can only activate 1 "Onomatopick" per turn. When this card is activated: You can add 1 "Onomato" card from your Deck to your hand, except "Onomatopick". You can target 1 "Zubaba", "Gagaga", "Gogogo", or "Dododo" monster you control that has a Level; have the Level of every monster you control become the targeted monster's Level, for the rest of the turn. You can only use this effect of "Onomatopick" once per turn.
